snippet.title: Turbo Leaper Demo 2 Trailer
snippet.description:
The Winter Challenge opens in the second demo for Turbo Leaper!

With refined graphics and special crossovers, the game expands!

Launching through SFGHQ on December 8.

TURBO LEAPER original game by RIEGELSOFT.

A NEW ALTERNATIVE CHAPTER by PhilRaco.

SUPER FREAKS by SuperFreaksDev & KingNormal.
B.U.D.D. by EngineerKappa.
Mr. Shootem by defnotreal_ and The Shooteam.
Tacti-Cat by NULL3D.
Prototype N by Arrietty.
Super Player World by Pvic.
